br />\n<br />\n終有一日，我地會喺街頭、煲底相見。<br />\n勿忘初心、勿忘手足、齊上齊落。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:47:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"04ab01295d312802d5a17481d934e3d0f4579a3c","tid":2291402,"uid":373515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a18f828e9320e6aeb0b5bc88d5d8b6c7f6e5c14","tid":2291402,"uid":373515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"一年前發生嘅事，你仲記唔記得？<br />\n<br />\n1,377位手足被捕，318位手足被要求登記，成為單日最多拘捕人數的一次。<br />\n<br />\n狗方一共使用4發實彈、4823發催淚彈、4532發橡膠子彈、839枚布袋彈、778枚海棉彈，共10976發彈藥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gm3hCfH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGm3hCfH.jpg&h=11395d95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VXGSq83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVXGSq83.jpg&h=fb79ed47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsHaXfK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzsHaXfK.jpg&h=3ca0a593&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7BMi585.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7BMi585.jpg&h=153f1640&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebEdaAL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FebEdaAL.jpg&h=f25cb07b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XiHY586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXiHY586.jpg&h=a587e226&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBqjQAO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBqjQAO.jpg&h=49d11c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/urotJVO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FurotJVO.jpg&h=8d8a0de3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKLWSPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKLWSPa.jpg&h=d8846d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一年。<br />\n理大圍城事過境遷，但好多手足嘅前途、生命永遠從此停留理大，<br />\n有手足患上創傷後遺症、被控暴動候審、流亡海外...，<br />\n當年十八歲以下同坐救護車出去嘅自首手足，仲要繼續提心吊膽被隨時清算嘅可能。<br />\n<br />\n面對民族創傷同痛苦，我地可以做啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1.繼續聲援被捕手足。</strong><br />\n雖然而家經已冇咗街頭抗爭，看似回復平靜，但其實血腥暴力嘅事仍然每日上演，講緊嘅就係每日庭上嘅審訊，港共利用司法制度每日折磨殘害手足。<br />\n<br />\n面對極長而且獨裁嘅審訊，你嘅支持會成為手足最大嘅安慰同力量。tg:@youarenotalonehk (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5ohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=43aa86d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a>) 每日都會update手足上庭時間表，手足可以按時到場聲援。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2.緊記歷史，留住真相。</strong><br />\n對家務求洗白，將會不斷歪曲改寫歷史。你以為有好多人會有智慧明慎思辨，事實上就係會有一堆人會被&rdquo;brain-washed&rdquo;，以訛傳訛，最後達成對家將謊言成為主流嘅目的。故此，我地必須記錄歷史，將真相廣傳，俾所有人認清事實。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">最後，最緊要係勿忘初衷。</span><br />\n呢大半年，好多人都俾武肺同埋国安法推行而磨蝕心志，社運彷彿亦走到低潮，但願你記得昔日齊上齊落嘅感動、感受手足嘅痛苦，緊記沉冤待雪嘅梓樂、彥霖，將感受同痛苦成為你前行嘅動力。<br />\n<br />\n2014，我地講過話We will be back。<br />\n2019，我地最終真係開展咗浩浩蕩蕩嘅流水革命。<br />\n<br />\n終有一日，我地會喺街頭、煲底相見。<br />\n勿忘初心、勿忘手足、齊上齊落。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:47:39.000Z","msg":"自推！"},{"pid":"a75f79bb5e6b99b130cc81d081fac4a8898b09af","tid":2291402,"uid":373515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a18f828e9320e6aeb0b5bc88d5d8b6c7f6e5c14","tid":2291402,"uid":373515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"一年前發生嘅事，你仲記唔記得？<br />\n<br />\n1,377位手足被捕，318位手足被要求登記，成為單日最多拘捕人數的一次。<br />\n<br />\n狗方一共使用4發實彈、4823發催淚彈、4532發橡膠子彈、839枚布袋彈、778枚海棉彈，共10976發彈藥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gm3hCfH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGm3hCfH.jpg&h=11395d95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VXGSq83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVXGSq83.jpg&h=fb79ed47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsHaXfK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzsHaXfK.jpg&h=3ca0a593&s={SIZE}\" /><i